      Changed lots of text and slight layout alteration.
      
      Added access to non-registered users, except you can't change much.
      
      New GUI library.
      
4.5 - Bumped version number.

4.4 - Bumped version number to match MagicFile.

4.3 - Re-wrote loads of little bits, I think it's alot better now! :o)

4.2 - Optimised the code & fixed a few bugs.

